{
  "title": "Mildly Tangy Kenyan Fenugreek Curry",
  "description": "A tangy and aerated Kenyan curry featuring fenugreek, made with beurre-monte for a rich flavor, perfect for a weeknight dinner",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
  "diet": [
